dc_title_s: Parks Fond du Lac County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents parks for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2021.[The Parks layer depicts Parks and Recreation Trails in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin. Parks are copied from the Parcel layer.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.fdlco.wi.gov/departments/departments-f-m/land-information/data-download
